message.body: Have you heard from Brian? How is he feeling today?
Haven't heard. How are you?
I know why the caged bird sings
I'm ok, you know, lots to think about. And why does the caged bird sing?
Because it can see all the beauty outside the cage and knows that someday it will escape. Slavery.
Ok, why do you mention it?
I have no idea where that came from
? How are you?
Good, frustrated with work but good. Lots to do today...
How are you pretty lady?
You think you'll be Late again? Im still ok even after you told me about the caged bird :)
I listened to it at work. Steph (Pip) got a job and I said I'd go celebrate for a little bit and since we (yes, we) skipped out on brunch and I dont have my car to get there alone...
The cost is one can of garbanzo beans to get out of it and it looks like you're in the negative there
I'll give you two! I have a bunch of stuff I have to do after work too ...
What kind of stuff?
Mail, bank, library, packing
I guess groceries can wait
Ok then. Well have fun in Texas! Drive safe!
Not funny with the sarcasm
Trust me I'm not laughing
But hey, I could use a ride to my car if that's possible otherwise I can bus to it
I'm really sorry! Probably will be home in an hour
I know, so you can give me a ride or no?
Not fir another hour or so
And just so I know, then you have stuff to do or would you be able to come with?
I could put it off
Is it stuff I could do for you when you're gone?
I'm sorry I've been so cranks. I'm really not feeling good and its making me feel like the world's going to end.
Don't say that! Are you feeling physically sick or just down?
Physically sick, regina and Kristina are out today and minas kids are sick so aomethings going around. How are you?
(01/02) I'm sorry Marth, hope you feel better. Go home if you need to! I am tired and wish you wouldn't have fallen asleep so quickly last night but totally und
(02/02) erstand. Just missing you
I dont really remember falling asleep at all, you should've woke me up! Bob said he'd give me a ride if I want to go home but then nobody would be here. How are you?
You were out immediately and snoring and beautifully peaceful so I couldn't wake you. Like I said, tired ane missing yoj but having fun!
Snoring? Sorry I asked twice. Im glad youre having fun though and very proud of my cabinet making secret boyfriend.
Non secret! Doing a crossword!
Send me clues
Piece for orchestra and soloist. 8 letters
Concerto
Does it work?
Yes! Legendary Gaelic bread?
No idea about Gaelic bread. Ugh Tuesdays. Was I really snoring last night?
Yes! Beautifully
Beautifully? But I don't normally right?
Nope but it was kinda sweet. How bout jiminy cricket declaration?
Oh! Gaelic BARD
How many letters for jiminy cricket?
8. Second is m third is n
Not sure about either but I can look them up
I feel really bad about falling asleep so fast
No worries mattie. Of course I wanted you to stay up a little later but you needed it. Are you still guest clinicianing?
I know but I want as much time with you as possible. Yea I am tonight
Dude, you should have borrowed my iPod
Word. But we've been talking the whole time. No time to sleep or music
That's a lot of yacking. I hope Sammy doesn't think I'm too much of a mess. Or worse, a bore.
Not at all. At the art institute right now, just heard something that made me think of you, I'll tell you later
Why can't you tell me now? I'm glad you arrived safely.
(01/02) Well its a complicated series of thoughts but basically ends with me being incredibly moved by the fleeting beauty of your piano playing. You are an ama
(02/02) zing woman. Feeling better?
That's really sweet of you. Yea I'm not feeling super but better. Just got out of the master class.
What have you boys been up to?
Just got back from a massive urban hike. Kinda a stressful day. Sleep well pretty lady and feel better
Oh man, tourism? I'm singing at an open mic which maybe is not so smart. Sweet dreams :)
Let me know when you're planning on getting home kiddo
Niiice! What you singing?
Poison and wine
What? Poison? Like every rose has its thorn? Take care of yourself missy
Do you know when you'll be home?
Hope by 7!
You hope as in not likely?
As in for sure
Travel safe today sweets
Already on the road. You feeling better?
Yea I feel better, i drank water like a fish and slept like a warrior last night. Green tea now. Caffeine, I'm a daredevil I know. How are you?
Hey green tea! We are outside Madison, and I'm sick of driving!
I bet. That's a lot for just two days. Sleep or think about life, or try and name all 50 states, or write me a love letter.
How far are you?
Coming into the cities and then gotta go to the rental place so maybe home by 6?
Nice. What's the rental place?
Oh van stuff
We rented a van and gotta take my boss there and home
Which home are you going to?
The one by your house but gotta take Sammie home too
What time so you go into work?
830 why?
How serious were you about not going?
You can't! Let's plan on tomorrow
Ok. I guess you'd want to sleep this morning anyway. But ugh.
Could you really go?
I'm trying with Reg. But if you have to get to work then don't wait for me
Well I definitely have to take Sammie, that's why we gotta plan ahead
How do you mean? Like for tomorrow
Ya
My back hurts like the rap songs say
Why? Don't know that phrase
From doing it! Reg says that she wants me to take time off!
Are you alive?
Yessss ! That's great news. How about all day tomorrow?
Can you get off all day?
Is that some kind of innuendo? Either way, a big yes
Welllllll hey! What about lunch with the boss man?
When will you be done? I'm working late for a bit
Done! Before you!
Oh damn! Want to pick me up? :/
Sure, when?
No you don't have to, it's crazy. Maybe I'll take the bus though
Ok well let me know. I told Ross 7 for grilling. Did you get work off tomorrow?
I don't need my car right? And yea it'll be fine. Did you?
Yesss!
